{"tid":1741551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘇格蘭國際發展局投資主任港人鄭文傑稱 不斷有香港示威者被送到中國內地拘禁","createTime":"2019-11-20T11:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T15:05:59.000Z","uid":41861,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2467b6622a1508cf24cdd3a60db608483432c2af","tid":1741551,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:33:05.000Z","msg":"曾於英國領事館任職蘇格蘭國際發展局投資主任嘅港人鄭文傑 （Simon Cheng），今年8月8日喺深圳工作後，坐高鐵回港時被捕，其後羅湖警方指鄭文傑因嫖妓被行政拘留15日。<br />\n<br />\n今日Simon喺Facebook發出聲明，交待自己被拘留經過。佢指喺審問期間，曾被綁到鋼製嘅「老虎椅」上，被問到「英國於香港『騷亂』中嘅角色」、「佢本人於香港『騷亂』中嘅角色」及「佢本人同參加香港『騷亂』嘅人嘅關係」三條問題。Simon亦指拘留時曾被命令企幾個鐘，當佢瞓著時就會被迫唱中國國歌，發言時亦要先講「報告，我嘅主人」，否則就會被打。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">喺其中一次審訊時，Simon被帶到「集體調查中心」連同約10名年輕嫌疑犯接受審問。佢表示審問期間聽到有公安以廣東話問：「舉起手！你係咪喺示威中揮旗？」，Simon估計當時有香港示威者正被審問，更指有表示自己係秘密警察向佢清楚表面，不斷有香港示威者被送到中國內地拘禁。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSimon喺接受BBC訪問時表示，英國已向佢批出兩年工作證，但佢認為保護不足，仍然嘗試尋求庇護，現時已經離開香港及離職。<br />\n<br />\nSimon喺聲明最後強調，即使日後將要面臨危險、歧視、報復及聲譽受損，佢自己一生都唔會放棄爭取人權、和平、自由與民主。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100most/photos/a.292832474177740/2461419327319033/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100most%2Fphotos%2Fa.292832474177740%2F2461419327319033%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=38729ebe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100most/photos/a.292832474177740/2461419327319033/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"a4fdbee97c36b6886c0a64d839b203d2bab07a7f","tid":1741551,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651e81aa5e348afaec37bbb7e9a8291d3551f06d","tid":1741551,"uid":129537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67d806adb67c54277ba8ba3cd34ff3997c147b6","tid":1741551,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a758284eb2d9e8e55aff14998af167e6767b69ff","tid":1741551,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:36:59.000Z","msg":"sm啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"0fa2f84e8964d91e5cd7f5720d726305ef7276bc","tid":1741551,"uid":251945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a74067069a3fe4689d94b47880652970a9c229","tid":1741551,"uid":57211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bfcfe534b024328acc3cb6959e38f3b324cc45","tid":1741551,"uid":247483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989fb1490afab8a0971e3ca26209e7472365c456","tid":1741551,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"LorraineC 絲打可能都俾國安捉咗上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff22f37d8db8511a3cf162ad6e50988ba5465738","tid":1741551,"uid":41861,"like":0,"